OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1776780669
OL,3,CAt least two children die each month
OL,4,Cfrom knife injuries in England, study
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FIt also reveals a rise in knife-
OL,8,Frelated fatalities among children
OL,9,Funder 17. Across the country, 21
OL,10,Fchildren died from knife crime-related
OL,11,Finjuries in 2019/20. That number rose
OL,12,Fto 36 in 2023/24.
OL,14,FThe two studies have shed light on
OL,15,Fknife crime by examining victims'
OL,16,Fsocial backgrounds and the violence
OL,17,Fthey were exposed to before their
OL,18,Fdeaths.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1776780669
OL,3,CAt least two children die each month
OL,4,Cfrom knife injuries in England, study
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FIn the first study, researchers from
OL,8,FBristol Medical School examined the
OL,9,Fdemographics and injuries associated
OL,10,Fwith the deaths of 145 children and
OL,11,Fyoung people under the age of 18 who
OL,12,Fdied from knife wounds in England
OL,13,Fbetween April 2019 and March 2024.
OL,15,FResearchers analysed data from the
OL,16,FNational Child Mortality Database
OL,17,F(NCMD) together with hospital, social
OL,18,Fcare and police data to identify
OL,19,Fpotential strategies to reduce the
OL,20,Fnumber of knife fatalities.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1776780669
OL,3,CAt least two children die each month
OL,4,Cfrom knife injuries in England, study
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FOf the 145 lives lost, 90% were male,
OL,8,Fwith an average age of 14.4 years, and
OL,9,Fthree-quarters of the victims were
OL,10,Ffrom areas facing the greatest levels
OL,11,Fof poverty.
OL,13,FAround one third (32%) of those who
OL,14,Fdied were black, and another third
OL,15,F(31%) were white.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1776780669
OL,3,CAt least two children die each month
OL,4,Cfrom knife injuries in England, study
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FWhen analysed on a population basis,
OL,8,Fyoung people of black or black British
OL,9,Fethnicity were around 13 times more
OL,10,Flikely to die of knife-related injury
OL,11,Fthan children and young people who
OL,12,Fwere white.
OL,14,FMost children who were victims of
OL,15,Fknife-related deaths were involved
OL,16,Fwith statutory services before injury.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1776780669
OL,3,CAt least two children die each month
OL,4,Cfrom knife injuries in England, study
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FOf the 57 cases available for detailed
OL,8,Fanalysis, injuries to the chest and
OL,9,Fneck caused 75% of deaths, and 60%
OL,10,Fdied before reaching hospital. Two-
OL,11,Fthirds of those who died suffered a
OL,12,Fsingle stab wound.
OL,14,FResearchers found that adverse
OL,15,Fchildhood experiences were common
OL,16,Famong young people, with a history of
OL,17,Fdomestic violence and abuse being the
OL,18,Fmost frequent.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1776780669
OL,3,CAt least two children die each month
OL,4,Cfrom knife injuries in England, study
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FA quarter of children (24%) lived with
OL,8,Fan adult with mental illness, and
OL,9,Fnearly a third (31%) lived in a
OL,10,Fhousehold with substance abuse.
OL,12,FGang involvement was mentioned in a
OL,13,Fthird of case files, and concerns
OL,14,Fabout carrying knives were recorded in
OL,15,Fa quarter (25%) of cases.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1776780669
OL,3,CAt least two children die each month
OL,4,Cfrom knife injuries in England, study
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe researchers said the findings
OL,8,Findicated the group at highest risk of
OL,9,Fexperiencing a fatal stab wound in
OL,10,FEngland were young people of black
OL,11,Fethnicity who live in urban areas of
OL,12,Fdeprivation.
OL,14,FLead author Dr Tom Roberts, an A&E
OL,15,Fclinician at North Bristol NHS Trust,
OL,16,Fsaid: "Knife-related fatalities among
OL,17,Fchildren and young people are a
OL,18,Fsignificant public health concern.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1776780669
OL,3,CAt least two children die each month
OL,4,Cfrom knife injuries in England, study
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"Our research identifies where action
OL,8,Fcould be taken to prevent future
OL,9,Ftragedies and demonstrates the urgent
OL,10,Fneed to support children facing
OL,11,Fadversity and marginalisation.
OL,13,F"Despite frequent contact with
OL,14,Fservices, many children received no
OL,15,Ftargeted support for adverse childhood
OL,16,Fexperiences, especially domestic
OL,17,Fviolence and abuse, revealing major
OL,18,Fgaps in early intervention."
OL,26,@zD@\O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1776780669
OL,3,CAt least two children die each month
OL,4,Cfrom knife injuries in England, study
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FCo-author Dr Edd Carlton, also an A&E
OL,8,Fclinician at North Bristol NHS Trust,
OL,9,Fadded: "Our findings show how
OL,10,Fdangerous carrying a knife can be, a
OL,11,Fsingle stab wound can prove fatal.
OL,13,F"It also emphasises the urgent need
OL,14,Ffor prevention strategies that address
OL,15,Fthe social, environmental, and
OL,16,Fstructural factors behind these
OL,17,Fdeaths."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1776780669
OL,3,CAt least two children die each month
OL,4,Cfrom knife injuries in England, study
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe second study examined the
OL,8,Fcircumstances around the 58 deaths of
OL,9,Fchildren under 18 in England who died
OL,10,Ffrom knife injuries between 2019 and
OL,11,F2024 and had detailed NCMD case files.
OL,13,FThe research explored how and why
OL,14,Fthese children died, and the different
OL,15,Ftypes of violence they may have been
OL,16,Fexposed to at home, school or in their
OL,17,Fcommunities.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1776780669
OL,3,CAt least two children die each month
OL,4,Cfrom knife injuries in England, study
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F58 children who died had experienced
OL,8,Fsome form of violence or harm during
OL,9,Ftheir lives. Many were both victims
OL,10,Fand perpetrators in different
OL,11,Fsettings, the home, school, or
OL,12,Fcommunity, but services often focused
OL,13,Fonly on one aspect of their experience.
OL,15,FLead author Dr Jade Levell, from the
OL,16,FUniversity of Bristol, said: "Our
OL,17,Fanalysis shows that many of these
OL,18,Fchildren experienced multiple forms of
OL,19,Fviolence across home, school, and
OL,20,Fcommunity before their early deaths.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1776780669
OL,3,CAt least two children die each month
OL,4,Cfrom knife injuries in England, study
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"Although it is not possible to
OL,8,Fconclusively say whether a specific
OL,9,Fintervention would have made a
OL,10,Fdifference, it is plausible to believe
OL,11,Fthat appropriate interventions that
OL,12,Facknowledge the extent of violence
OL,13,Fcutting across different domains of
OL,14,Fhome, school and community in some
OL,15,Fchildren's lives could have made a
OL,16,Fpositive difference."
OL,18,FThe Government said it has committed
OL,19,Fto halving knife crime in a decade.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
